product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:130:- Create a natural incentive to choose the rewarded-ad option when the user wants faster progress.
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:131:- Limit unlimited free reward farming while preserving learning value.
