product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:144:- The system must not block gameplay when the base reward decreases.
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:145:- The base reward decrease must be communicated as a daily reward state, not as punishment.
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:146:- The rewarded-ad option remains available after each completed Attempt when ad availability and external reward logic allow it.
